# Project Rules

Full details: see AGENTS.md at project root and .opencode/skills/ for deep-dive guides.

## Commands

- `npm run check` — lint + typecheck + format:check (run before committing)
- `npm run test:run` — Vitest unit tests
- `npm run build` — production build (must pass)
- `npx vitest run path/to/file.test.tsx` — single test

## Critical Rules

1. **Max 250 lines per file.** Extract into sub-files if exceeded.
2. **No hardcoded colors.** Use design token Tailwind classes (`bg-primary`, `text-muted-foreground`). Tokens in `src/app/globals.css`.
3. **Arrow functions** for UI components. **Function declarations** for pages/layouts.
4. **Named exports** for components (`export { Button }`). `export default` only for pages/layouts.
5. **Always** destructure `className`, spread `...props`, wrap classes with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`.
6. **`"use client"` only when needed** — hooks, event handlers, Radix primitives.
7. **Import order:** (1) `"use client"`, (2) third-party, (3) `@/` aliases, (4) relative.
8. **No axios.** Use `api()` from `@/lib/api.ts` (typed fetch wrapper).
9. **Co-locate files.** Route-specific → `_components/`. Shared → `components/`. Types used <3 files → inline.
10. **JSDoc** on every exported component/function.

## File Placement

- UI components → `src/components/ui/` + add to `index.ts` barrel
- Pages → `src/app/{route-group}/{route}/page.tsx`
- API routes → `src/app/api/{resource}/route.ts`
- Schemas → `src/lib/schemas.ts` (split at >10)
- Hooks → `src/hooks/use-{name}.ts` + add to `index.ts` barrel
- Actions → `src/lib/actions.ts` (split at >5)
- Tests → `{source-dir}/__tests__/{name}.test.tsx`

## Formatting

Double quotes, semicolons, trailing commas, 2-space indent, 100 char width, Tailwind class sorting.

